---
title: Roasted Veg, Chorizo and Lentil Jumble with Feta, Toasted Almonds and Herby Drizzle
description: The nature of a jumble is to mix all the ingredients for a beautiful blend of flavours. Our roasted veg and lentil variation is a Middle-Eastern inspired dish made with sweet and fragrant spices and a slight kick of heat thanks to the chilli. Sweet potato, aubergine and tomatoes are a great match for the earthy and nutty flavour of lentils. Finish off with a sprinkling of tart feta mixed with lemon and toasted almonds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-veg-chorizo-and-lentil-jumble-16605b05-8cbdb486.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/roasted-veg-chorizo-and-lentil-jumble-610160ac0ea55e1cd504d287-b7028478.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/roasted-veg-chorizo-and-lentil-jumble-610160ac0ea55e1cd504d287
course: main course
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
time required: 45m
nutrition:
  calories: 814 kcal
  fat: 46 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
  carbohydrates: 62 g
